                            <comment id="12650395" author="fern" created="Tue, 25 Nov 2008 00:05:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;this is actually a bigger diff of cleaning up the scopes of more pom files..&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;some dependencies are set to be &quot;compile&quot; when they really are hard dependencies ( runtime ), and some dependencies are compile when they should be &quot;provided&quot; so that they are not actually required unless the end-user explicitly uses them ( hsqldb, postgresql, etc )&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12650610" author="mikedd" created="Tue, 25 Nov 2008 16:13:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the patch. There&apos;s a lot of opportunity for cleanup in the pom.xml files I&apos;m sure.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
